## Win/Loss Intelligence

### Why Customers Choose Them Over Us

**Primary reasons:**
1. **[Reason 1]** ([%] of losses cite this)
   - **Context:** [When this matters]
   - **Mitigation:** [How to prevent]

**Example (Why customers choose Confluence):**
1. **Atlassian ecosystem lock-in** (60% of losses)
   - **Context:** Already use Jira, Bitbucket, Opsgenie
   - **Mitigation:** Qualify Atlassian dependency early, show our Jira integration

2. **IT mandate for on-premise** (25% of losses)
   - **Context:** Regulated industries, data residency requirements
   - **Mitigation:** Qualify cloud-ok early, walk if hard on-premise requirement

3. **Existing Confluence investment** (15% of losses)
   - **Context:** Multi-year contract with Confluence, switching cost too high
   - **Mitigation:** Position as complement not replacement, start with new use case

### Why Customers Choose Us Over Them

**Primary reasons:**
1. **[Reason 1]** ([%] of wins cite this)
   - **Context:** [When this matters]
   - **Amplify:** [How to emphasize]

**Example (Why customers choose Notion over Confluence):**
1. **Speed to value** (70% of wins)
   - **Context:** SMBs need team productive now, not in 3 months
   - **Amplify:** Show live demo, "You can start using this today"

2. **All-in-one vs point solution** (60% of wins)
   - **Context:** Teams using Confluence + Asana + Google Docs + spreadsheets
   - **Amplify:** "Confluence is just wikis. We're wikis + tasks + docs + databases"

3. **No IT required** (55% of wins)
   - **Context:** Small teams without dedicated IT resources
   - **Amplify:** "Confluence requires IT for weeks. We're self-serve in 2 hours"

